   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"(Christian sign) It is your servant Joseph who ventures to write to the glory of your lordship . . .  . Your lordship has told me . . . take them. As for that which is in the list of . . . inform me of them in order that I may see that . . . outside  . . .   ."</ab>
         </div>
